org.glassfish.contextpropagation.wireadapters

Class Catalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.contextpropagation.wireadapters.Catalog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Catalog
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains metadata that identifies the each context entry on a stream. This information helps recover from an unrecoverable IO error when reading context-propagation data from a stream. It makes it possible to skip a corrupted context.
    See Also:
